    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先画出三个节点：A是欺诈检测，B是支付网关，C是总账服务。A指向B，B指向C。",
      "elements_involved": [
